3/11_large.png?m=1651565926","name":"linux","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6512/bd43/11_normal.png?m=1651565926","title":"Linux","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/linux","topics":7018,"footer":"","header":"Linux is a Unix-like computer operating system assembled under the model of free and open source software development and distribution.","title_alternative":"Linux","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6512/bd43/11_mini.png?m=1651565926","stars":5948,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":11,"parent_node_name":"os"},"member":{"id":557492,"username":"documentzhangx66","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/documentzhangx66","website":null,"twitter":null,"psn":null,"github":null,"btc":null,"location":null,"tagline":null,"bio":null,"avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/f59c/d92e/557492_mini.png?m=1662992998","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/f59c/d92e/557492_normal.png?m=1662992998","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/f59c/d92e/557492_large.png?m=1662992998","created":1633180949,"last_modified":1662992998},"last_reply_by":"KKLeon","last_touched":1667734297,"title":"PVE-WIndows 建议不要安装 360 安全卫士","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/893081","created":1667722389,"deleted":0,"content":"PVE 7.2-11\r\nWindows 10 企业版 20H2\r\n360 安全卫士 13(13.0.0.2004)，备用木马库：2022.11-05\r\nvirtio-win-0.1.221.iso\r\n\r\n问题说明：\r\n360 安全卫士，自动把 virtio-win 的下面几个驱动，当成木马删了。\r\n\r\nC:\\Windows\\System32\\drivers\\balloon.sys\r\nC:\\Windows\\System32\\drivers\\netkvm.sys\r\nC:\\Program Files\\Virtio-Win\\Balloon\\blnsvr.exe\r\nC:\\Program Files\\Qemu-ga\\qemu-ga.exe\r\nC:\\Program Files\\Virtio-Win\\VioFS\\virtiofs.exe\r\n\r\n\r\n在恢复区里，把被删除的条目，进行恢复并信任。但重启后，网卡仍然没了。\r\n\r\n重装 virtio-win 驱动后，Windows 10 开机时，直接蓝屏：\r\nINACCESSIBLE BOOT DEVICE 。","content_rendered":"<p>PVE 7.2-11\nWindows 10 企业版 20H2\n360 安全卫士 13(13.0.0.2004)，备用木马库：2022.11-05\nvirtio-win-0.1.221.iso</p>\n<p>问题说明：\n360 安全卫士，自动把 virtio-win 的下面几个驱动，当成木马删了。</p>\n<p>C:\\Windows\\System32\\drivers\\balloon.sys\nC:\\Windows\\System32\\drivers\\netkvm.sys\nC:\\Program Files\\Virtio-Win\\Balloon\\blnsvr.exe\nC:\\Program Files\\Qemu-ga\\qemu-ga.exe\nC:\\Program Files\\Virtio-Win\\VioFS\\virtiofs.exe</p>\n<p>在恢复区里，把被删除的条目，进行恢复并信任。但重启后，网卡仍然没了。</p>\n<p>重装 virtio-win 驱动后，Windows 10 开机时，直接蓝屏：\nINACCESSIBLE BOOT DEVICE 。</p>\n","last_modified":1667722389,"replies":10,"id":893081},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_large.png?m=1650095340","name":"qna","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_normal.png?m=1650095340","title":"问与答","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna","topics":192521,"footer":"","header":"一个更好的世界需要你持续地提出好问题。","title_alternative":"Questions and Answers","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1650095340","stars":3606,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":12,"parent_node_name":"v2ex"},"member":{"id":595245,"username":"vanvan00097","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/vanvan00097","website":"","twitter":null,"psn":null,"github":null,"btc":null,"location":"","tagline":"","bio":"","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/9edc42eed271d952612ee1013b319a74?s=24&d=retro","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/9edc42eed271d952612ee1013b319a74?s=48&d=retro","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/9edc42eed271d952612ee1013b319a74?s=73&d=retro","created":1664008792,"last_modified":1664544395},"last_reply_by":"sevenyangcc","last_touched":1667716070,"title":"大家看 S12 了吗？","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/893036","created":1667702576,"deleted":0,"content":"目前 1：1 感觉 都是旗鼓相当的对手。期待一个 3：2 打满 BO5 让世界记录这疯狂的时代","content_rendered":"<p>目前 1：1 感觉 都是旗鼓相当的对手。期待一个 3：2 打满 BO5 让世界记录这疯狂的时代</p>\n","last_modified":1667702576,"replies":10,"id":893036},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_large.png?m=1630643913","name":"apple","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_normal.png?m=1630643913","title":"Apple","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/apple","topics":20506,"footer":"","header":"设计了 <a href=\"/go/